+Updated stale runtime package tests to match the corrected `.d.ts` generation behavior. Declaration snapshots and substring assertions now expect `declare const` readonly declarations and `export declare const artifacts`, and tests no longer require missing method notices to render as the literal string `undefined`.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
