+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateRuntime.spec.ts:95 - Updated inline dts runtime snapshot to declaration-style output.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateTevmBody.spec.ts:255 - Updated inline dts body snapshot to declaration-style output.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateTevmBody.spec.ts:611 - Assert missing method notices do not render as `undefined`.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateTevmBodyDts.spec.ts:60 - Updated dts body inline snapshots for readonly declaration output.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateTevmBodyDts.spec.ts:305 - Updated dts substring assertions for declaration-style contract names and ABIs.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/generateTevmBodyDts.spec.ts:377 - Assert missing method notices do not render as `undefined`.
+- bundler-packages/runtime/src/extended-tests.spec.ts:103 - Updated complex struct dts expectation to declaration-style contract name output.
